Text:
Informing you that his Does Not Work,
Or not on my system at least.

Ok i have retested most of the stuff i said earlier that was not working, 
There seems a problem on some Mac machines with 7z.
I have now used this one:http://www.macupdate.com/app/mac/19139/ez7z

And all are opening, installing & working.

1. unzip with ez7z only. 
2. install. 
3. register with any 18 digit serial
4. click manual registration
5. enter unlock code generated by included keygen. 
6. click never register.
